        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/building-study.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/building-study.html",
            "title": "Building Study",
            "summary": "The design of the buildings around my school in Manhattan had interesting&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/17/gallery/ComfyUI_00494_.png\" data-size=\"1656x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/17/gallery/ComfyUI_00494_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"575\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/17/gallery/20251106_103728-2.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/17/gallery/20251106_103728-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>The design of the buildings around my school in Manhattan had interesting architecture, and this was more of appreciation for the simple yet elegant design. I used this sketch for further testing of using an already made layout of the general structure of the image to see how AI would add elements to the composition.</p>",
