        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/mighty-giant-enters-the-sketch.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/mighty-giant-enters-the-sketch.html",
            "title": "Mighty Giant Enters the Sketch",
            "summary": "When i was learning to draw the world around me, I drew&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/ComfyUI_080418_494996367663489_00039.png\" data-size=\"1584x1056\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/ComfyUI_080418_494996367663489_00039-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/ComfyUI_075937_847805584681167_00036.png\" data-size=\"1584x1056\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/ComfyUI_075937_847805584681167_00036-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/ComfyUI_00473_.png\" data-size=\"1656x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/ComfyUI_00473_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"575\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/20251106_111501.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/gallery/20251106_111501-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>When i was learning to draw the world around me, I drew everything. This is an unfinished study of a SUV on the street of my dorm in Manhattan at F.I.T college. My perspective is off on the car view that is why you keep drawing and strengthening your ability to translate the world onto paper. I used this sketch with AI testing its ability to tell a story around my original elements of the drawing. For this test of AI my first thought was to test something AI struggled to create which was the concept of just seeing a giant's feet. Once I had the feet, something was missing, so i added some characters to the concept, which then lead to the final idea to have them looking up to tie all elements together into a cohesive story.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/16/ComfyUI_080418_494996367663489_00039.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "Characters",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-05T17:50:04-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T17:53:22-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/egyptian-city-sketch.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/egyptian-city-sketch.html",
            "title": "Egyptian City Sketch",
            "summary": "My creative process usually starts with a very rough outline of the&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/15/gallery/ComfyUI_00483_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/15/gallery/ComfyUI_00483_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/15/gallery/20251106_043427.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/15/gallery/20251106_043427-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>My creative process usually starts with a very rough outline of the general composition. This was an idea to incorporate tanks which can be found in hieroglyphs into a collage of perspectives using some ideas of art from the  Egyptian walls and layering that with depth in the flow of the image from top to bottom. I never got further with this concept so this was fun to give to AI and see if it got my idea with minimal prompting. This is my strength in the modern world with technology, the ability to sketch an idea and now hand it off to an AI and have a partner in the creative process. Being able to communicate ideas with drawings helps to drive a concept easier then trying to just prompt directions and hope the AI get the idea. Visual ques from something as simple as this sketch and you can see it got the picture of what i was thinking for each layer.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/15/ComfyUI_00483_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-05T17:21:02-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T17:30:32-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/dog-problems.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/dog-problems.html",
            "title": "Dog Problems",
            "summary": "This is just a playful interaction of a flea and a dog.",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/14/gallery/ComfyUI_00460_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/14/gallery/ComfyUI_00460_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/14/gallery/ComfyUI_00393_.png\" data-size=\"1760x1176\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/14/gallery/ComfyUI_00393_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"513\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/14/gallery/scan0003.jpg\" data-size=\"953x1626\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/14/gallery/scan0003-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1310\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is just a playful interaction of a flea and a dog. I am actually pretty happy that I never colored in so much work, leaving me with perfect layouts to learn about the power of AI. The AI images I was experimenting with seeing how it colored in the picture based on my prompts and for these I was testing how it used paint to complete the picture. I was looking for the texture of the paint will keeping the detail of the beads of sweat.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/14/ComfyUI_00460_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Characters",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-05T17:16:24-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T17:16:24-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/big-bang-comedy-tour.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/big-bang-comedy-tour.html",
            "title": "Big Bang Comedy Tour",
            "summary": "The concept for this logo was to create the energy and feel&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p> </p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00144_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00144_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/IMG679.jpg\" data-size=\"1280x960\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/IMG679-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00145_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00145_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00146_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00146_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00147_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00147_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00151_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00151_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>The concept for this logo was to create the energy and feel of big and showing a bang and the typical bomb explosion cloud around a microphone I feel sells the idea, while relating to the mental visual picture created by this combination of words and imagery. This logo I used to test a few styles changes to see how AI handles this kind of imagery. Then I used AI to apply the logo concept to a mock-up location. I did not try to refine the logo with these images, I was more interested in AI ability to apply styles to words and imagery.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/13/Qwen_Edit_2511_00157_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Logo Design",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-05T01:10:41-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T01:11:25-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/the-fresh-twist.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/the-fresh-twist.html",
            "title": "The Fresh Twist",
            "summary": "This logo concept was fun to create, I love logo's because it&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p> </p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/thefreshtwist_logo_by_rudytrnka.png\" data-size=\"340x198\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/thefreshtwist_logo_by_rudytrnka-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"340\" height=\"198\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/Flux2-Klein-4b-base_00004_-2xl.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/Flux2-Klein-4b-base_00004_-2xl-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00039_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00039_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/IMG_0283.JPG\" data-size=\"3264x2448\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/gallery/IMG_0283-thumbnail.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This logo concept was fun to create, I love logo's because it takes all artistic ability and revolves around something that needs to be readable as a logo, yet have some flare to stand out. I find logo's a good test of creative ability. For the fresh twist logo I wanted something that evoked the name fresh with a design that felt fresh as well. I first do sketches of ideas for logo before entering the digital space. This logo was finished in Photoshop and revived with AI to test AI ability to maintain the logo, while creating a mock-up of the logo applied to a real world situation.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/12/Flux2-Klein-4b-base_00004_-2xl.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Photoshop",
                   "Logo Design",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-04T23:30:53-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T00:27:08-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/groovin-elephant.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/groovin-elephant.html",
            "title": "Groovin Elephant",
            "summary": "This is from my studies of mixing characters with surreal concepts to&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/11/gallery/ComfyUI_00444_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/11/gallery/ComfyUI_00444_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/11/gallery/scan0033.jpg\" data-size=\"1558x2070\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/11/gallery/scan0033-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1020\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is from my studies of mixing characters with surreal concepts to create a movement of the viewers eyes around the image looking for the little hidden details. I like to create an energy or flow of lines and color that make you want to see every detail of the image, trying to make something as simple as an elephant dancing into something with some visual depth of the image and the meaning behind it. The fish are the music manifested into matter swimming into the elephants ear. The more colored version was a light edit with an AI model to see if it could keep the feel of the image and add a little something extra.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/11/ComfyUI_00444_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Characters",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-04T22:22:04-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-04T22:25:36-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/connecticut-nature-study.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/connecticut-nature-study.html",
            "title": "Connecticut Nature Study",
            "summary": "I have always had a sketch book with me where ever I&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/10/gallery/ComfyUI_00626_.png\" data-size=\"1656x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/10/gallery/ComfyUI_00626_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"575\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/10/gallery/20251106_105645.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/10/gallery/20251106_105645-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>I have always had a sketch book with me where ever I went, and this was from a long road trip, just enjoying the hills. I was inspired by the long branch when i drew the sketch and also inspired by the long branch to create a composition that featured and accented that feature of the drawing. The first thing that came to mind was a disco ball and the rest just came together</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/10/ComfyUI_00626_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Characters",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-04T21:37:44-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-04T21:37:44-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/music-store-flyer.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/music-store-flyer.html",
            "title": "Music Store Flyer",
            "summary": "This flyer was hand drawn for client, they requested me to make&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/9/gallery/ComfyUI_00458_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/9/gallery/ComfyUI_00458_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/9/gallery/cd-store-flyer-design-lg.jpg\" data-size=\"462x600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/9/gallery/cd-store-flyer-design-lg-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"462\" height=\"600\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This flyer was hand drawn for client, they requested me to make the flyer with my style of whimsy.  This was a test of AI to see how it would handle text with minimal direction. I would rerun this with more direction for the darker area, I include this sample because as is, its still a fun example for color choices by AI.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/9/ComfyUI_00458_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Print Design",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-04T21:24:04-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-04T21:24:04-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/chillin-cat-in-wonderland.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/chillin-cat-in-wonderland.html",
            "title": "Chillin Cat in Wonderland",
            "summary": "This is an old sketch done using a marker, no pencil, each&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/8/gallery/ComfyUI_00461_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/8/gallery/ComfyUI_00461_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/8/gallery/ComfyUI_00394_.png\" data-size=\"1760x1176\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/8/gallery/ComfyUI_00394_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"513\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/8/gallery/scan0005.jpg\" data-size=\"1513x2110\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/8/gallery/scan0005-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1071\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is an old sketch done using a marker, no pencil, each line is permanent. This was an old practice sketch of  image within image challenging myself strengthening my creative mind learning to make choices and stick with them. I will be circling back to this image with AI and experimenting with different methods to create a finished image.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/8/ComfyUI_00461_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
